  "body": "The vsphere volume [calls out to cloud provider to attach a volume](https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/master/pkg/volume/vsphere_volume/vsphere_volume_util.go) as part of the `setup(...)` step in the `mounter` plugin interface. \n\n_The vsphere volume plugin should be refactored to implement the volume [`Attacher` plugin interface](https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/master/pkg/volume/volume.go#L136)._ This will enable it take advantage of the attach/detach controller and let volume_manager better control device mounting (prevent multiple concurrent operations, do retries, etc).\n\nCC @abithap\n",
